<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Low Stock Alert - Book'Insat</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .alert {
            background: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Low Stock Alert</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="alert">
        <h2>Stock Level Warning</h2>
        <p>The following book is running low on stock:</p>
        <p><strong>Book Title:</strong> {{ bookTitle }}</p>
        <p><strong>Current Stock:</strong> {{ currentStock }} units</p>
    </div>

    <p>Please review the inventory and restock if necessary.</p>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from Book'Insat Inventory Management System.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 